<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2023/05/twig-96/ffc397da4fb5541a7ee9cf7ff874536976b98249.png" alt="" />
</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@0xmrtt:envs.net">0xMRTT</a> says</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://imaginer.codeberg.org">Imaginer</a> 0.2.1 has been released with <a href="https://imaginer.codeberg.page/help/custom">support of custom provider</a>, an improved UI, a faster loading mechanism for Preferences, and an improved mechanism for saving credentials.</p>
<p>You can download Imaginer from <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/page.codeberg.Imaginer.Imaginer">Flathub</a> or from either <a href="https://github.com/ImaginerApp/Imaginer">Github</a> or <a href="https://codeberg.org/Imaginer/Imaginer">Codeberg</a>.

