</p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@imansalmani:matrix.org">Iman Salmani</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://github.com/iman-salmani/iplan">IPlan 1.1</a> is out.
this is a solution for managing your personal life and workflow (its a goal).
you can download it from <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/ir.imansalmani.IPlan">flathub</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Features</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Grouping tasks with project and list</li>
<li>Timer for tasks</li>
<li>Global search</li>
<li>Arranging projects, lists and tasks by drag and drop</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>changes in this version</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Lazy loading for project tasks and stat</li>
<li>Records window for create, edit and delete records

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2023/05/twig-96/MFwEHOZgEsByXnwfBfiMCBtD.png" alt="" />
</li>
</ul>
